snippet.title: Killing Floor 3 - Gameplay Trailer | PC Gaming Show 2024
snippet.description:
Get a new look at all of the guns and gore coming to undead shooter Killing Floor 3.

Killing Floor 3 is coming to PlayStation, Xbox, and PC in early 2025.
